"```sql\nSELECT \n    (SUM(CASE WHEN y.Date = '201208' THEN y.Consumption END) - \n     SUM(CASE WHEN y.Date = '201308' THEN y.Consumption END)) / \n    SUM(CASE WHEN y.Date = '201208' THEN y.Consumption END) AS consumption_decrease_rate\nFROM \n    transactions_1k t\nJOIN \n    yearmonth y ON t.CustomerID = y.CustomerID\nWHERE \n    t.Amount = 634.8 AND \n    t.Date = '2012-08-25';\n```"